  "detailed_description": "This video captures the complete transformation of a client's hair and beard at a professional barbershop. The process begins with initial shaping using clippers and scissors, followed by precise scissor work on damp hair. The barber then incorporates Reuzel hair tonic for conditioning, and blow-dries the hair to achieve volume. Beard foam is applied and styled, concluding with pomade application for the final slicked-back look. The video culminates in the client's satisfied reaction and a showcase of his sharp, classic hairstyle and well-groomed beard.",
